Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为戏剧社是文化社
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演戏可是格斗技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 为什么要在室外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是服务粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务粉丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这里演出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得音箱还是放那座时钟的位置比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 介绍一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准社员之一 青木翼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.35,0:02:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是自行车社的 对机械特熟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出时帮忙负责音响和照明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来当演员也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱系需求很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我做后台就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我演技完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐会手把手脚把脚地教你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不必…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 实在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准社员虽多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过知道素体秘密和绮罗星存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有我们6人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼同学
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 会有点痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 脸色有点差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是有烦恼？翼同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 怎么知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师一直都很关心学园里的每个学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里也做心理疏导
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都可以跟我商量哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧 被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是健康食品公司的开发研究员
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得跟冈本老师挺般配的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是年龄有点偏大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在没有对象的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见个面也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈本老师还是喜欢美少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:04:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学…学园长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您为什么会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…这些是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈本老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹治惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 惠都同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的名字也请您记一记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是化学实验社的部长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而老师您可是顾问哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 最近忙晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好像有人擅自拿走社团柜子里的药品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得想个对策才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可是个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种您不训斥一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻违反校规来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有对脑波的反馈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以干涉独立时间轴的素体Yodock（腕）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和零时空间这个舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我们科学协会的技术才得以实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是终极的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样必能打败Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后我们将掌握绮罗星的主导权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个装置是有我们科学协会的驭星者格林教授
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能够完成 这点不可不提
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是作为大学部的研究员来这座岛上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何格林要当学园保健医生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔着玻璃可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子主动 真是下贱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得可爱又有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是不是受欢迎过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这气味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气味？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.39,0:08:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 这个气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会变成那女生的男后宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男后宫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,600)}（和子妄想中）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不不 不至于那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)}（你怎么知道的）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 她在看拓人和须方了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媚…媚眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次在日常生活中见到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非接下来是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.79,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.71,0:09:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞吻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是现实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们学校有那女生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 那女生好有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要挖来戏剧社
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是地震
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是气多岛在震动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女生不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩子 好像在哪儿见过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时间真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 我是担心刚才的地震会不会打破瓶子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是顾问嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走曼德拉草媚药的果然是老师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.23,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼德拉草？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师对学生出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经不仅是校规的问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绮罗星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是格林教授吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是沉醉…是沉醉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用迷人的气味俘虏异性的曼德拉草媚药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有十几岁的年轻人服用才会发挥效力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但十几岁的年轻人真喝下去就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是现实中无法使用的媚药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有身为Yodock驾驭者的你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在现实中使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种支配力想用来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想尝尝你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很相像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们学园的毕业像册
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是十几年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫冈本翠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.32,0:11:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那位保健医生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是十几年前了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.68,0:11:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有驭星者可以用第一阶能力返老还童
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是绮罗星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但听说那是会对周边时空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成扭曲的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计正因为滥用那种能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最近地震频发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气多封印被解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气多岛上的火山也开始活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最坏的情况 或许会喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气多岛喷发 对这里造成伤害的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也应该困扰才对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他们并不知道那种能力和地震的关联性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在滥用第一阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向许多男生发出了邀请信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是放在须方书桌里的信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很要命的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀请男生去做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为所欲为？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:12:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我假装接受邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去刺探情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有收到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷地「被」为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之用我的方式调查下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信 读了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏力？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给其他人发了不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有不少
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只发给喜欢的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的男生 有多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘～密～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近好频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果附近的火山岛喷发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受今宵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.79,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这地震是你的缘故？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你使用的能力 在招来这灾害？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发地震违反校规？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.41,0:14:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为我们绮罗星十字团的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗会更加惨烈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.71,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理准备的话一早就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想尝尝你的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有渴望得到的东西就别犹豫！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.89,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了乌贼大王的栖身地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是终年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狂风暴雨肆虐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被危险的滔天大浪包围的海域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连乌贼刺客大人也对这次航海心生顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是少女这样训斥了萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 面对真正想要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以顾虑于风险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位少女 说得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌贼刺客萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把少女留在海边小屋中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独自开始危险的航海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生的冒险还在继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.10,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启 电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆水的巫女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 今天是你的死期了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科学协会的所谓新兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两把星剑的冲击是9万8千L
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超乎预料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能正面承受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预知模式
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看见 能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.71,0:19:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个系统可以在零时空间内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预见几秒以后的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格斗战中的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绝对性的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂～巨腕！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动太完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气决出胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换模式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,450)}（预知模式 > 观赏模式）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纤细的腰骨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄壮的胸板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 下面会怎么来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪快…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二头肌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脖颈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～锁骨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斩！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪快银河十文字斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果没猜错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得入迷 被干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.26,0:21:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 觉得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 正宗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口还疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.53,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能要求心理疏导吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢上老师了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里就难受得不得了
